Ingredients:
    Chocolate Pack x1
    Strawberry x2
    Sugar Pack x2
    Milk Bottle x1
    Butter Can x1
    Flour Pack x1
    Egg x3
Steps:
    COOKIES:
        Add to Mixing Bowl and Mix using Stand Mixer
            Chocolate x1(Place Chocolate Pack on table and E to open)
            Sugar 150g
            Flour 400g
            Egg x3

        Extract from Mixing Bowl
            Heart Cookie
    MIXTURE:
        Add Mixing Bowl and Mix using Stand Mixer
            Butter 200g
            Strawberry Slice x4
            Sugar 150g
            Milk 0.20 lt
    Add to a heart cookie
        Heart Cookie Mixture x3

    Bake in Oven
        Heart Cookie

    Cool in Fridge

    Transfer to Plate
        Heart Cookie x3
        
    Serve  Cool